<br />
<span style="color: red"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal">Pet Heal Cycles</span></span>
<br />
<span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal">*note the heal over time is not included in this analysis</span>
<br />

<br />
Chaining 44 and 52 heals results in a cycle of:  8.5 seconds heals 960 HP for 475 mana 
<br />
Healing per second: <span style="font-weight: bold">112.9</span> 
<br />
Efficiency: <span style="font-weight: bold">2.02</span> HP per mana 
<br />

<br />
Therefore, a level 52 magician can combat any MOB that has a DPS lower than <span style="font-weight: bold">112.9</span> as long as he has mana.
<br />

<br />
Chaining 52 and 60 heals results in a cycle of: 12 seconds heals 1480 HP for 675 mana 
<br />
Healing per second: <span style="font-weight: bold">123.33</span> 
<br />
Efficiency: <span style="font-weight: bold">2.19</span> HP per mana 
<br />

<br />
Therefore, a level 60 magician can combat any MOB that has a DPS lower than <span style="font-weight: bold">123.33</span> as long as he has mana.
<br />

<br />
Chaining 60 and 64 heals results in a cycle of: 15 seconds heals 2100 HP for 700 mana
<br />
Healing per second: <span style="font-weight: bold">140.00</span> 
<br />
Efficiency: <span style="font-weight: bold">3</span> HP per mana 
<br />

<br />
Therefore, a level 65 magician can combat any MOB that has a DPS lower than <span style="font-weight: bold">140.00</span> as long as he has mana.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Thanks to Master Eandori Raintree for the original impetus to compile this information</span><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26797">Sage Jaytee Bushwacker [Fires of Heaven]</a> 
<br />
65 Arch-Mage, <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/tower/viewtopic.php?t=3239">Magician's Tower Librarian</a>
